to act in the best interests

00:04:30.650 --> 00:04:35.290
of the nation abroad and how
they might do so in the future.

00:04:35.290 --> 00:04:39.470
This evening our speakers will
consider the delicate balance

00:04:39.470 --> 00:04:44.640
