One during the dramatic hours

00:10:40.570 --> 00:10:44.620
when President Bush was unable
to return to Washington.

00:10:44.620 --> 00:10:49.110
Reporting for all ABC News
broadcasts, Compton has traveled

00:10:49.110 --> 00:10:53.450
