00:47:37.510 --> 00:47:43.280
So I said, "Let's have
a joint hearing --

00:47:43.280 --> 00:47:45.050
House and Senate together.

00:47:45.050 --> 00:47:47.070
I'll come over to your shop."

00:47:47.070 --> 00:47:49.510
We had to go to the
Speaker to get that done

00:47:49.510 --> 00:47:51.070
