00:47:51.070 --> 00:47:53.590
And Tip O'Neill looked
as us both and said,

00:47:53.590 --> 00:47:54.940
"What the hell's wrong with that?"

00:47:54.940 --> 00:47:56.240
And we did.

00:47:56.240 --> 00:47:59.170
I think we had twenty
joint hearings.

00:47:59.170 --> 00:48:01.050
Covered a lot of ground.

00:48:01.050 --> 00:48:04.970
Kennedy was my ranking member.

00:48:04.970 --> 00:48:08.050
Sonny Montgomery was over
there in the Democrats,

00:48:08.050 --> 00:48:10.660 position:56%
Ham Fish -- good, thoughtful people.

00:48:10.660 --> 00:48:14.580
The vote was bipartisan.

00:48:14.580 --> 00:48:19.230
And then I remember very
swiftly I was still in the Senate

00:48:19.230 --> 00:48:22.430
